          "_name": "article03",
          "_sourceTheme": "preschoolm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article03\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n        <header>Text</header>\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"textAmount\">\n            <option value=\"0\">0</option>\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>2</option>\n        </select>\n        <header condition=\"showImage\">Image</header>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Height\" name=\"imgHeight\" min=\"1\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\" condition=\"showImage\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/preschoolm5/components/_images/bg/3-bg.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/preschoolm5/components/_images/bg/1-bg.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"row mb-3\">\n                <div class=\"col-12\">\n                    <div class=\"p-2\">\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                            <b>Mauris mattis metus sit amet ultricies feugiat.</b>\n                        </h2>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row {{contentAlign}}\">\n                <div class=\"card col-12\">\n                    <div class=\"card-body p-2\">\n                        <img class=\"card-img mb-4\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/2-people.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n                        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\">\n                            Brain Training Games for Children\n                        </h3>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text text1 mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text.text1\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" mbr-if=\"textAmount > 0\">\n                            Morbi in lorem nibh. Fusce aliquam pulvinar sapien, at iaculis lectus congue sit amet.\n                        </p>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text text2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text.text2\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" mbr-if=\"textAmount > 1\">\n                            Sed sed venenatis neque. Nunc vestibulum velit vulputate, ultricies nisi sit amet, dictum\n                            felis. Quisque eget aliquam augue. Quisque ut dolor vehicula massa aliquam sagittis quis a\n                            quam. Mauris tempor consectetur efficitur. Aenean ornare turpis ut sodales blandit.\n                            <br>\n                            <br>\n                            Donec sodales diam in ex viverra faucibus sit amet vitae ex. Proin non consequat metus.\n                            Mauris bibendum dui ut libero placerat, vel auctor magna tincidunt. Proin ex tortor,\n                            pharetra a luctus sit amet, vulputate at diam. Nulla blandit neque at magna vulputate\n                            lobortis. In lobortis fermentum mattis. Aenean erat sapien, aliquam et convallis eu, dictum\n                            sed eros. Pellentesque iaculis faucibus arcu vitae tristique.\n                            <br>\n                            <br>\n                            Mauris erat sem, dictum ut tincidunt id, varius eget nulla. Interdum et malesuada fames ac\n                            ante ipsum primis in faucibus. Nullam velit ipsum, porttitor quis tempor maximus, eleifend\n                            eu nisl. Duis a orci vel velit dignissim volutpat non eget elit. Phasellus quam mi,\n                            dignissim pellentesque mollis sit amet, luctus euismod arcu. Praesent sodales justo risus,\n                            non venenatis ante tincidunt sit amet. Etiam vitae mattis dolor. Etiam cursus ullamcorper\n                            pretium. Nam id fermentum dolor, nec bibendum enim. Sed vehicula nunc sit amet lectus\n                            faucibus, vitae cursus enim iaculis. Aliquam viverra id arcu vel varius.\n                            <br>\n                            <br>\n                            Integer ut vulputate magna, a consectetur augue. Aenean vitae lacus sed elit molestie\n                            sagittis. Aliquam ullamcorper sapien augue, venenatis mattis eros malesuada in. Proin vitae\n                            auctor erat. Nulla a rutrum turpis. Donec tempus eros sit amet arcu consequat, sit amet\n                            blandit elit viverra. Donec dapibus lorem et congue tempus. Etiam pellentesque lacus quis\n                            massa porta suscipit. Cras faucibus nunc id enim ornare elementum. Maecenas in metus justo.\n                            Maecenas aliquet hendrerit consectetur.<br><br>Integer ut vulputate magna, a consectetur augue. Aenean vitae lacus sed elit molestie sagittis. Aliquam ullamcorper sapien augue, venenatis mattis eros malesuada in. Proin vitae auctor erat. Nulla a rutrum turpis. Donec tempus eros sit amet arcu consequat, sit amet blandit elit viverra. Donec dapibus lorem et congue tempus. Etiam pellentesque lacus quis massa porta suscipit. Cras faucibus nunc id enim ornare elementum. Maecenas in metus justo. Maecenas aliquet hendrerit consectetur.<br>\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "u6lf2rUD8o",
          "_anchor": "article03-81",
